          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1607347806043-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>smashed avocado</strong>,<strong> chopped coriander</strong> and<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and gently mix<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>avo salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1607347810907-x200.jpg",
