            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1607347810907-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is tender, scoop the <strong>softened flesh</strong> out of the skins with a spoon – this is your <strong>pulled aubergine</strong></p><p>Tip: Carefully hold the stalks (they will be hot!) to scrape the flesh out easily</p><p>Discard the skins</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1607347866536-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1607347866536-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1607347866536-x700.jpg",
