          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1607347876741-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled red cabbage</strong>, discard the liquid</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1607347892351-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1607347892351-x400.jpg",
